    <div class="col_md_6_text">
      <div class="customer_store_info_text">
        <h3>Take your business <br>to the next level.</h3>
        <strong>Online and in- store</strong>
        <p>
        World Payments is designed to work seamlessly for faster customers’ usage of the sale system. Our system works on iPad, Mac, and PC, whether you are online or offline. It connects to the modern hardware including barcode scanners, receipt printers, cash drawers. Through our immediate responses in the selling point system, your clients will find It easy and fast to purchase and sell more to your customers. 
        </p>
        <strong> In-store world payments POS </strong>
        <p>
        Connect your online store with Vend, and manage your inventory and customer profiles from your pc. Sync your products, and bring all your business operation into Vend. In a few minutes, you are in control over everything - the small and the big details. 

        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clear_e"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row_e">
    <div class="col_md_6_img_r mobile">
