          <img src="/assets/pos/online_store_img2.svg">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col_md_6_text_l">
        <div class="customer_store_info_text">
          <h3>Widen your business</h3>
            <p>
              World payment system helps you stay ahead of your competitors by providing accurate information of transaction at every step including sales and products performance, that is accessible anytime and anywhere. Insightful reporting tools keep you informed about the details of customers, products, inventory, and staff. All this can be easily accessed with one click.
          </p>
          <p>
            You can easily manage one or hundreds of stores. Build your empire by adding new stores with easy registration by one click from your home. Staff training and motivation can also be performed through our system. All the safety and security of data is guaranteed.
          </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col_md_6_img_r desktop">
        <div class="customer_store_info_img_r r_img">
          <img src="/assets/pos/online_store_img2.svg">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clear_e"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row_e">
    <div class="col_md_6_img">
      <div class="customer_store_info_img p_l40">
        <img src="/assets/pos/online_store_img3.svg">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col_md_6_text">
      <div class="customer_store_info_text">
        <h3>Accept any and every type of Payment</h3>
        <p>Vend ensures that you get the payments easily. Set up custom buttons for the cash, cards, gift cards, checks or any other type of payment that is your requirement. Payments on Layaway sales, partial payments, deposits or account – the choice is yours.</p>
        <p>Accept credit or debit cards, mobile payments through phones or card machines. You can easily connect to PayPal or Worldpay or Square (to name the few) to your Vend POS system and you are good to go.</p>
        <p>POS can be easily understood, train your staff in a few minutes, keep them motivated all the time. Then relax know that with POS it’s always safe, secure, and available anytime you need it </p>

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clear_e"></div>
  </div>

  
</section>
